[1 - 4] - select the appropriate card of the digit which you pressed
[ENTER] - use selected card
[W] - move the selected unit one tile up
[S] - move the selected unit one tile down
[A] - move the selected unit one tile back
[D] - move the selected unit one tile forward
[E] - see the range of the use a unit's ability
[F] - see unit stats
